product_desc: Blue Box Laundry Services is going to be a residential and commercial laundry service company.  Blue Box Laundry Services will be able to pick up your dirty laundry clothes in a plastic blue container box to wash and fold them in a quick affordable way.  The box will have a toll free number with an automated and live operator where you will be able to call when you want your clothe picked up for washing and folding.  We'll have your clothe clean, folded, and delivered back to you in less than an hour.
